        notes: "Night's Watch deserter who led a band of brigands in the wolfswood south of Winterfell. A bald man with a raw windburnt face. He and others attacked Bran Stark in the wolfswood and held him hostage. Killed by Theon Greyjoy with a broadhead arrow through the chest."
